OL,3,CFather handed six-year prison term for
OL,4,Cfatal crash during 'cocaine comedown'
OL,6,FA father who caused a woman's death by
OL,7,Fdriving dangerously after taking
OL,8,Fcocaine has been jailed for six years.
OL,10,FChristopher Lynn, from Dalkeith,
OL,11,FMidlothian, drove into the back of a
OL,12,Fcar driven by Yvonne Nichol on the A7
OL,13,Fnear Ashkirk, causing it to swerve on
OL,14,Fto the opposite carriageway and
OL,15,Fcollide with an oncoming vehicle.
OL,17,FMs Nichol, 64, was taken to hospital
OL,18,Fbut died a short time later, while the
OL,19,Ftwo occupants of the other car were
OL,20,Fseriously injured in the incident on
OL,21,F15 August, 2023.
