OL,3,CFather handed six-year prison term for
OL,4,Cfatal crash during 'cocaine comedown'
OL,6,FThe High Court in Edinburgh heard Lynn
OL,7,Fwas driving at 81mph seconds before
OL,8,Fthe impact with Ms Nichol's car, and
OL,9,Fwas in the "comedown" phase after
OL,10,Ftaking cocaine.
OL,12,FLynn, 32, pleaded guilty to causing
OL,13,Fdeath by dangerous driving at a
OL,14,Fhearing at the High Court in Glasgow
OL,15,Fearlier this month.
OL,17,FAs part of the charge he admitted
OL,18,Fdriving "while impaired having
OL,19,Fconsumed cocaine", and driving at
OL,20,F"excessive speed".
