OL,3,CFather handed six-year prison term for
OL,4,Cfatal crash during 'cocaine comedown'
OL,6,FLord Clark sentenced him to six years
OL,7,Fbehind bars and disqualified him from
OL,8,Fdriving for nine years when the case
OL,9,Fcalled on Thursday, with Lynn
OL,10,Fappearing by video-link from HMP
OL,11,FBarlinnie in Glasgow.
OL,13,FThe judge said the crash happened in a
OL,14,F60mph zone but Lynn should have been
OL,15,Frestricted to 50mph, because he was
OL,16,Fdriving a light goods vehicle.
