OL,3,CFather handed six-year prison term for
OL,4,Cfatal crash during 'cocaine comedown'
OL,6,FHe told him: "You had ingested cocaine
OL,7,Fand you were on the comedown from
OL,8,Fcocaine, which can cause a lack of
OL,9,Fconcentration, distraction and
OL,10,Ffatigue."
OL,12,FHe said victim impact statements from
OL,13,Fthe families of Ms Nichol and other
OL,14,Fvictims were "harrowing" to read.
OL,16,FLord Clark said: "There is no sentence
OL,17,FI can impose that can in any way
OL,18,Falleviate the devastating consequences
OL,19,Fof your actions for the individuals
OL,20,Fand the family members."
