OL,3,CFather handed six-year prison term for
OL,4,Cfatal crash during 'cocaine comedown'
OL,6,FHe told Lynn that if he had been found
OL,7,Fguilty at trial he would have jailed
OL,8,Fhim for eight years, but he reduced
OL,9,Fthis to six due to his early guilty
OL,10,Fplea.
OL,12,FAdvocate Victoria Dow, representing
OL,13,FLynn, said the father-of-one had
OL,14,Fpreviously led a "blameless and
OL,15,Fworthwhile life".
OL,17,FShe told the court: "He is a man who
OL,18,Fdeeply regrets his behaviour that led
OL,19,Fto this devastating accident.
